        "Description": "Agent 47,\ryou smell that ?\r\rThis is a mixture of sweat &amp; spiciness and frankly some tears. A whole buffet of bad decisions meet you as today&apos;s main course in the heart of Mumbai. This time,you will move some brutal, holy, hairy and hot spirits through the alleys.\rSubtlety is encouraged, but not mandatory. In such a place where noise is constant, the wrong silence can be the loudest statement - and a well timed accident can make the best storytelling.\r\rTikka Ma Fella 47!\r\rCheeeers,\rBuuuurgers",
